      <title>欧洲央行推出数字欧元以回应特朗普推动加密货币政策</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ecb-pitches-digital-euro-response-trumps-crypto-push-2025-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员皮耶罗·西波洛内周五表示，欧元区银行需要数字欧元来响应美国总统唐纳德·特朗普推动稳定币的举措，稳定币是一种通常与美元挂钩的加密货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ecb-pitches-digital-euro-response-trumps-crypto-push-2025-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:42:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国鸿山能源以 11.5 亿美元收购马歇尔集团股份，Telia 出售</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-hongshan-buys-majority-stake-marshall-group-115-bln-deal-2025-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洪山资本集团（HSG）周五表示，已达成协议，将收购马歇尔集团的多数股权，该交易对这家总部位于斯德哥尔摩的音响设备制造商的估值为 11 亿欧元（11.5 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-hongshan-buys-majority-stake-marshall-group-115-bln-deal-2025-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
