      <title>假日消费强劲推动美国运通收入超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/amex-profit-jumps-resilient-credit-card-spending-2025-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国运通周五公布的第四季度营收超出预期，原因是节日期间更多消费者刷卡旅行和网上购物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/amex-profit-jumps-resilient-credit-card-spending-2025-01-24/</guid>
